         <div type="edition">
            <ab>
               <lb n="1"/>
                  <supplied reason="lost">
                     <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan>
                     <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan>
                  </supplied>
               <lb n="2"/>
                  <persName>
                     <name type="praenomen" key="Lucius"><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan></name>
                     <name type="gentilicium" key="Publicius">Publicius</name>
               <lb n="3"/>
                     <name type="cognomen" key="Epitynchanus">Epitynchanus</name>
                  </persName>,
               <lb n="4"/>
                  <persName>
                     <name type="cognomen" key="Perennius">Perennio</name>
                  </persName>
               <lb n="5"/>
                  filio dulc
               <lb n="6" break="no"/>
                  issimo, 
                  <expan><abbr>vix</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan>
               <lb n="7"/>
                  <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>nis</ex></expan>
                  <num value="8">VIII</num>,
                  et suis
               <lb n="8"/>
                  fecit.
            </ab>
         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p> To the divine shades. Lucius Publicius Epitynchanus made [this] for [his] most dear
               son Perennius, [who] lived for eight years, and for his own.</p>
         </div>
